go-shuffle-shard
----------------
This package implements the "simple signature" version of Amazon's Shuffle
Sharding technique for load balancing and fault isolation.
Shards generated by this implementation are probabilistic and derived from a
hash of identifiers.

  * Reference:     https://github.com/awslabs/route53-infima.
  * Documentation: https://godoc.org/github.com/clickyotomy/go-shuffle-shard
